headline: GTA Online
subtitle: A NEW YEAR’S GIFT
content: All together now: We wish you a Festive Beerhat, we wish you a Firework Launcher, we wish you some New Years Glasses and a happy new year! Oh, and 20 Firework Rockets, Full Snacks, Full Armor, 25 Sticky Bombs, 25 Grenades, 5 Proximity Mines and 10 Molotovs…
